2/ Requirement:

+ Remove all files in "folder_02"
+ Open file "ex_04.bash" by "VI" and compose a short script so as to find all files in format of "file*V0*v"  to "folder_02" and rename to follow an order:
  
   XXX_V44.v is corresponding to file_V01_T01.v
   XXX_V33.V is corresponding to file_V02_T02.v
   XXX_V22.V is corresponding to file_V03_T03.v
   XXX_V11.V is corresponding to file_V04_T04.v

+ Guide: Use commands "find" and "for"

3/ How to run

   ./ex_04.bash 

4/ Expected result 

